      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Ready for your next road trip? This well-maintained beauty is in great shape and ready to hit the pavement! It offers a smooth, reliable drive and has been cared for to ensure it stays dependable for years to come. While it shows the gentle character of a pre-owned vehicle, its solid performance and clean interior make it a fantastic find for anyone looking for quality and value. Come see why this reliable ride is the perfect fit for your lifestyle!",
