      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and is an ideal choice for someone prioritizing mechanical reliability over cosmetic perfection. The engine and transmission are in solid working order, ensuring a dependable driving experience for daily commutes. However, please note that there are visible signs of wear on both the exterior paint and the interior upholstery, including some minor scratches and fading. All major systems are functional, making this a practical and honest value for a buyer who needs a car that performs well on the road without the premium price of a showroom-ready model.",
