    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies. Mated to a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory limited-slip differential, the chassis remains taut with documented subframe reinforcement and refreshed bushings. The VANOS system has been professionally serviced, ensuring optimal variable valve timing across the rev range. This example presents in strong mechanical health with minor cosmetic wear consistent with its age, offering a visceral, high-revving driving experience.",
