    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained sedan offers the perfect balance of luxury and dependability. The exterior shines in a classic Deep Obsidian Black, showing only minor signs of road use like small stone chips on the front fascia, while the body remains straight and free of door dings. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary of premium charcoal leather; the seats are supple with only light wear on the driver\u2019s side bolster, and the genuine wood trim accents remain vibrant. Every feature\u2014from the panoramic sunroof and dual-zone climate control to the premium surround-sound system\u2014operates exactly as intended. Under the hood, the engine runs quietly and delivers power smoothly, backed by a comprehensive service history and a recent oil change and brake service. The vehicle sits on a set of high-performance all-season tires with approximately 70% tread remaining, ensuring a confident ride in all weather conditions. This is a turn-key vehicle ready for its next owner who values a well-cared-for, reliable machine.",
